Requirement :
  * modules (C version) : http://modules.sourceforge.net/

Install :
  * install module from source and add this line to bashrc :
    . /usr/local/Modules/3.2.7/init/bash

Configuration :
  * copy / create modulefiles into default search path (/usr/local/Modules/3.2.7/modulefiles/)
  OR
  * define a new search path (add this in bashrc) :
    module use ~/.modules

Usage :
(see http://modules.sourceforge.net/man/module.html)
  * module load java
  * module list
  * module avail
  * module unload java
